Creation correlation(创立相关)

        With the rapid development of economy and society, Chinese consumers'
attention and ability to health management are also improving. In the fast-paced development of society, people's social ways are also subtly changing, loneliness, interpersonal alienation and psychological problems have also emerged.

        (随着经济和社会的高速发展，中国消费者对健康管理的重视程度和能力也在提高。
身处快节奏发展的社会，人们的社交方式也在潜移默化发生改变，孤独感、人际疏离和
心理问题也相继萌发.)

        "Roll" does not move, and does not lie "flat" is the normal life of young
people. In this context, as The carrier of "healing economy" - plush toys, The Cutedoll seems to be a good medicine, in the hands of young people. After
all, who would say no to a doll with a smiling face? Soft, lovely, accompanying, healing, is synonymous with The Doll.

        (“卷”不动，又躺不“平”是年轻人的生活常态。而在这个大背景之下，作为
“疗愈经济”的载体--毛绒玩具，The Cutedoll仿佛一剂良药，正中年轻人下怀。毕
竟谁会对着一只长着微笑脸的玩偶say no呢？柔软、可爱、陪伴、治愈，是The Doll
的代名词。)

logo

        This is The logo of The Cutedoll company, a cute kitten wearing a scarf.
Ms. You, one of The founders of The Cutedoll company, is very fond of cats,
so the cat is the main element of the logo. The cat wears a warm scarf, which
also means the service tenet of The Cutedoll, warmth and cure every customer.

        (这是The Cutedoll公司的logo,一只戴着围巾的可爱小猫。The Cutedoll玩偶
公司的创始人之一尤女士对猫咪很是喜爱,因此将猫咪作为logo的主元素,小猫戴着温
暖的围巾也寓意着The Cutedoll服务宗旨.温暖治愈每一位顾客。)

Brand product(品牌产品)

        The Cutedoll product line mainly includes doll series, doll series and
art doll series, each series has its own unique design concept and cultural
implications. From traditional cultural elements to modern emotional
expressions, The Cutedoll has successfully transformed dolls into artistic
products with deep cultural significance and emotional value.

        (The Cutedoll的产品线主要包括玩偶系列、大偶系列和艺术偶等系列，每
一系列都有其独特的设计理念和文化寓意。从传统的文化元素到现代的情感表达，
The Cutedoll成功地将玩偶转化为具有深厚文化意义和情感价值的艺术产品。)

Brand concept(品牌理念)

        The core of the brand concept of The Cutedoll is "subversion of tradition, subversion of self". Thisconcept is reflected in The brand's reinterpretation of traditional culture and the clever integration of modern design,The Cutedoll
believes that only by constantly innovating and breaking through conventions
can we create truly vital works of art.

        (The Cutedoll的品牌理念核心在 于“颠覆传统，颠覆自我”。这一理念体现在
品牌对传统文化的重新诠释与现代设计的巧妙融合上,The Cutedoll相信，不破不立，
只有不断创新，突破常规，才能创造出真正具有生命力的艺术作品。)
